<br>
1)Crushed opals for Vel. Bracers- common drops or rare? Sent Armor/Co. drakes in CS drop or not? Cos tto buy on market?<br>
<br>
2)Ditto the crushed flame emeralds for boots<br>
<br>
Second set of questions-<br>
<br>
1)Can the gems be multiquested with leather parts<br>
<br>
I know (using kael) that you have to be ALLY to tormax to get armor.  If they can be multiquested, does the other person have to be an ally as well?<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaerillea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aerillea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 9:02:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crushed opals/crushed flame emeralds- common or uncommon</span><hr size=1> On the Tunare server<br>
<br>
Crushed Opals- <br>
About 1k to buy, rather common one of the crushed type.<br>
Best place to get, Velks zone in or sentient suits, if solo.  Groupwise, Velks lab.  <br>
<br>
Crushed Flame Emeralds- Since this is a gem that is shared with melee bracers, this is a hard one to get.  3k per emerald on my server.  Sentient suits and velks lab if solo.  Otherwise Icewell underdungeon if grouped.<br>
<br>
To multiquest- all members involved need to have the appropriate faction and/or level.  Had a pair of thurg leather gloves rotting in the bank and decided to give it a try.      <br>
<br>
1) Gave the gloves to the quest guy in the leather shop(I'm at ally)<br>
2) Gave him 2 crushed opals.<br>
3) Had another druid at amiable give one other crushed opal.  Did not receive gloves.<br>
4) Gave the quest guy one crushed opal, I received gloves.<br>
Needless to say, gloves I won't use sitting in the bank now =/<br>
<br>
I should have had it confirmed by killing the quest guy to see if he still had 1 crushed opal on him.  If he did, then it would further supplement that both characters need to be of the approriate faction levels. <p>Aerillea Mystfyre~

<br>Chere Amie of Team HLS

<br>60 Sexy Wood Elf Heirophant
<br>Co-Leader of Forbidden Prophecy.
<br>~Destiny is only a promise~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uziela.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ziela</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/13/01 9:39:06 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crushed opals/crushed flame emeralds- common or uncommon</span><hr size=1> Crushed opals seem to go for about 1k, crushed flame emeralds more like 6-10k which I in no way could afford so I went and camped suits in WL off and on for a week=p  Got something like 2 crushed flame emeralds, 1 crushed black marble, 2 crushed opal, 2 crushed onyx sapphire, crushed flame opal, and a bunch of junk gems (like crushed emerald, not used in any quests).  Doesn't seem like any one gem is rarer than the others, just that the drop is very random so it may take awhile to get those you need (and the demand for the emeralds is insane:( ) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udreth1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dreth1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 6:12:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crushed opals/crushed flame emeralds- common or uncommon</span><hr size=1> Hmmm... Is there a price guide on the safehouse. By guide, I know it's different for all the servers. More of a guideline?<br>
<br>
For example, are different armor sections worth more? I know chest armor gems are worth alot. What about legs vs. wrist vs. whatever?<br>
<br>
Any spots I can look? So far, search has been unsuccessful.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umistrylcorazon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mistryl Corazon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 8:19:32 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crushed opals/crushed flame emeralds- common or uncommon</span><hr size=1> Last night in Velk's camping the spiders for those @*&amp;# threads, we had a crushed opal, crushed flame emerald, and crushed sea sapphire (or something like that, I remember the sea part) all drop.<br>
<br>
We were there about 4-5 hours and killing the spiders on the ledges above.<br>
<br>
